column2: SELECT    m.obsid,    m.ra  AS lamo_ra,    m.dec AS lamo_dec,       o.ra  AS SDSS_ra,    o.dec AS SDSS_dec,    o.psfMag_u,     o.psfMag_g,     o.psfMag_r,     o.psfMag_i,     o.psfMag_z,   o.psfMagErr_u,  o.psfMagErr_g,  o.psfMagErr_r,  o.psfMagErr_i,  o.psfMagErr_z,    o.extinction_u, o.extinction_g, o.extinction_r, o.extinction_i, o.extinction_z,   o.clean,      n.objid,    n.distance    from MyDB.c AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #/#) AS n    JOIN Star AS o   ON n.objid = o.objid    into mydb.c_out
